name: Fishty Nine - A Math Game
description:
Fishty Nine is a game prototype created for Untitled Game Jam 69 with a theme of Numbers. 

Fishty Nine is a game about doing math and also some RNG.  The game level is partially generated at runtime including the target numbers you need to get through the level!  So each play through of the game will be different, accept for the end goal of scoring 69! 

This is far from a perfect game, but I plan to continue this project in the future, but jam deadlines got to be met!
